aVOr traditionally, the German education divides children
p225
aVat the age of 10, very young children,
p226
aVbetween those deemed to pursue careers of knowledge workers
p227
aVand those who would end up working for the knowledge workers,
p228
aVand that mainly along socioeconomic lines,
p229
aVand that paradigm is being challenged now too.
p230
aVA lot of change.
